      <scopecontent id="aspace_f01f04c336986772d4be2bba5b062b58">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of thirteen watercolors showing different scenes at the Yale Center for British Art, including views of the building's exterior and of sculptures inside it.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_77b878c5e4f9c6e31aa6755309124ee9">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Kevin Owens graduated from Yale with a Masters in Architecture in 1998. He was honored with the award for Royal Institute of British Architects Client of the Year 2012 for his work across the 2012 Olympics Games in conjunction with the Olympic Delivery Authority.</p>  
      </bioghist>
